{"word":"H3042 - יְדָיָה - Yᵉdâyâh - yed-aw-yaw' - Jedaiah","slug":"H3042","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְדָיָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yᵉdâyâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yed-aw-yaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jedaiah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>ידיה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yedâyâh</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yed-aw-yaw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jedaiah = \"praised of Jehovah\" <ol><li>a Simeonite, forefather of Ziza</li><li>son of Harumaph and one who took part in rebuilding the walls of Jerusalem</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H3034\">H3034</a> and <a href=\"#/H3050\">H3050</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1938\">H1938</a>, <a href=\"#/H1939\">H1939</a>, <a href=\"#/H1960\">H1960</a>, <a href=\"#/H3034\">H3034</a>, <a href=\"#/H3038\">H3038</a>, <a href=\"#/H3044\">H3044</a>, <a href=\"#/H8426\">H8426</a>"}]}